data.description: NEW PRICE!  DON'T WAIT!   Super cute split-level home in a great neighborhood on a dead end street.  Kitchen was remodeled in 2019 to include classy dark cabinetry and complimentary granite countertops, roof replaced in 2017, garage doors new in 2018; AC is 5 years old as is water heater. Larger lot with beautiful mature trees and spacious back yard.  All bedrooms are upstairs and master bathroom was remodeled in 2021. There is a separate dining room off the kitchen overlooking the comfy family room that features a massive rock fireplace, perfect for the upcoming cooler weather.  Convenient location in the northwest part of San Antonio.  Don't wait - call today to see!
